{"tid":1870570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家個天比機會你，但香港人仍然只識得被動","createTime":"2020-02-09T02:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T03:42:54.000Z","uid":285910,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ea43300c339b1449ae8812db72c950baef06fd","tid":1870570,"uid":285910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"有幾可支那可以一次過有<br />\n<br />\n貿易戰<br />\n豬瘟<br />\n鼠疫<br />\n肺炎<br />\n禽流感<br />\n<br />\n支那人對政府支持度前所未有咁低，連本地藍絲廢老都開始屌政府。<br />\n<br />\n跟著香港人做緊乜？日日瘋狂搵口罩，恥笑人買廁紙。手足人丁單薄都出黎做嘢搵命博，醫護唔怕秋後算帳都罷工守護香港，但連登熱門日日都係口罩/上面點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家就係反擊嘅時候。上面七國咁亂，點解唔襯佢病攞佢命？做文宣都得卦？輸出革命？twitter 啲retweet都跌到仆街，咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一日唔滅左支那共慘黨，每十年你就要炒一次口罩。我地可以創造奇蹟，但要視乎你有無心做。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油。"},{"pid":"8c4ada65b7a742860d236ce02342a87b8f3adbf0","tid":1870570,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb59b0e121228a126b109829b6b072fac97980e","tid":1870570,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4ada65b7a742860d236ce02342a87b8f3adbf0","tid":1870570,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:43:25.000Z","msg":"而家有啦<br />\n琴晚將軍澳打到飛起<br />\nDklm"},{"pid":"fc08edfb4ab89b1a0752af4ffa66e2de04dee1b6","tid":1870570,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb59b0e121228a126b109829b6b072fac97980e","tid":1870570,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4ada65b7a742860d236ce02342a87b8f3adbf0","tid":1870570,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 